data.description: NOTE:  Remodel valued at over $200,000 is almost complete!  Expected completion date: October 1, 2020.  (Pictures show current progress)  4 bedroom 3-bath house in Coconino Estates on a Corner lot.  Garage has been converted to make the large 4th bedroom or den.  But there is plenty of off street parking, plus a double back gate leading to a paved area in the backyard that is perfect for parking a boat, trailer, etc...  There is also a nice storage shed in the backyard.   Brand new roof in 2014.  Brand new Furnace in 2020.   Lots of beautiful Aspens in the Front Yard.  New redwood fence.  Close to Schools, trails and good coffee and pizza!  Very close to FMC and downtown.  This listing is a for sale by owner.  Owner is a licensed General Contractor.
data.whatILove: Currently being completely remodeled.  Projected Completion date: Oct 15, 2020.  Super desireable location in Coconino Estates!  Flagstaff's favorite neighborhood due to proximity to trails, schools, downtown and FMC.  Only 25 minutes or less to the bottom of Agassiz lift!!!  Walk or Bike to Downtown.  Close to Schools.  Corner Lot. Great neighbors too!  This remodel includes:  New furnace and ductwork.  New attic insulation.  Whole house exhaust fan.  Complete Electrical re-wire.  All new gas lines.  Complete remodel of Kitchen and all three bathrooms, including new cabinets, new granite counters, new faucets, new appliances, new lighting, high-end ceramic tile.  All the bedrooms have new ceiling fans with LED lighting and remote controls.  All new wood doors throughout the interior.  New front and rear doors.  New high-efficiency windows.  New spray foam insulation in kitchen, laundry and bath.  Double wall framing and sound dampening between den and Master Bedroom.  Expensive floor tile and tile base throughout entire house.  50amp 220v outlet for Electric Car charging.  New solar ready Electrical Panel.  All new interior paint.  New soaker tub in haul bath.  NEW, NEW, NEW.  This home is completely remodeled.  We expect to have the faucets, mirrors, appliances, shower doors and door knobs installed by the end of the month.  Note that the garage was converted to a 4th bedroom/bonus room.  However there is ample off street parking including a double gated drive for parking a boat or RV.  Also we replaced the roof about 6 years ago.  This house is in fantastic condition!
